(4009, 'client', 'contact-forgot-password', 'english', 'Forgot Password', 'Create New Password', '<h2>Create a new password</h2>\nForgot your password?<br /> To create a new password, just follow this link:<br /> <br /><a href=\"{reset_password_url}\">Reset Password</a><br /> <br /> You received this email, because it was requested by a {companyname}&nbsp;user. This is part of the procedure to create a new password on the system. If you DID NOT request a new password then please ignore this email and your password will remain the same. <br /><br /> {email_signature}', '{companyname} | SimplyIDo', '', 0, 1, 0, 72, 0, 27, '2018-03-23 02:15:34', NULL, NULL),
